    "title": "Blue Dart is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Junior)",
    "description": "Blue Dart invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of E-commerce Executive at our Ludhiana location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Blue Dart:\nBlue Dart is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ludhiana, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Blue Dart!",
